  <ul class="comments by_rank" >
      
      <li class="ctsh clearfix" data-cid="36753289">
        <div class="ilst">
          <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/65108637/"><img src="https://img1.doubanio.com/icon/u65108637-9.jpg" alt="宋薇棠" class="" /></a>
        </div>
        <div class="con">
          <div class="nlst">
            <h3>
              <div class="note-toggle rr">
                <a href="https://book.douban.com/annotation/36753289/" class="note-unfolder">展开</a>
                <a href="javascript:void(0);" class="note-folder">收起</a>
              </div>
              <a href="https://book.douban.com/annotation/36753289/" class="">第226页</a></h3>
          </div>
          <div class="clst">
            <p class="user"><a href="https://www.douban.com/people/65108637/" class=" " title="宋薇棠">宋薇棠</a>
                (微信公众号：wei-deep7)
              
                <span class="allstar40" title="推荐"></span>
            </p>
            <div class="reading-note" data-cid="36753289">
              <div class="short">
                
                  <span class="">游人稀少的花季清晨，满山满垄，消泯了声息，唯有光、风和煦的照拂，与光风携来、无处不在的芳香。

受光均匀的树冠，如华盖一般撑开，所以说“桂树中庭有午荫”，是真切而自然的记忆啊。</span>
                <p class="pl">
                  <span class="">2015-12-12 17:29</span>
                  
                    &nbsp;&nbsp;<span class="">2人喜欢</span>
                </p>
              </div>
              <div class="all hidden" style="display:none" >
                游人稀少的花季清晨，满山满垄，消泯了声息，唯有光、风和煦的照拂，与光风携来、无处不在的芳香。<div style="padding-bottom:1em;"></div>受光均匀的树冠，如华盖一般撑开，所以说“桂树中庭有午荫”，是真切而自然的记忆啊。
                  <div class="col-rec-con clearfix">
                    







<div class="rec-sec">

    <span class="rec">

